race.comment: JUST WALTER (1) is a leader who's been beaten a whisker here at his last two over this distance. Peaks and has a 3kg claim today and the speed to clear the wide gate. Can go one better. ZOUMAN ALONG (4) switches to synthetic for the first time. He was beaten 2.25L over 1400m at Gold Coast last time and will come on from that run. Peaks and is one of the best hopes. CHAYSE'N' THE KING (9) was outgraded at Doomben over shorter but was heading in the right direction prior. Third up and can feature. MAYOR OF KINGSTON (6) made good improvement stepping up to this distance at Ballina and will be fitter again. He can get into the money. CHAYSE 'N' LEISA (7) will find this easier than Doomben and has more to give. Should be around the mark.
